Flobopuyo - A clone of the Japanese PuyoPuyo game
---------

The goal of flobopuyo is to make groups of four or more Puyos (coloured
bubbles) to make them explode and send bad ghost Puyos to your oponent.
You  win the game if your oponent reaches the top of the board. You can
play against computer or another human.
The game has nice graphics and animations as well as  music  and  sound
effects.

You will need a filing system with long file name support to play this game.

Keys
----

Move Right		Right
Move Left		Left
Rotate			Up
Move Down		Down

This version created by the GCCSDK Autobuilder for details see:

http://www.riscos.info/index.php/GCCSDK#GCCSDK_Autobuilder

It also requires that the SharedUnixLibrary which is available from:
http://www.riscos.info/downloads/gccsdk/sharedunixlib/system.zip
